latestIgtvVideos.title: 💫 Set it free - An unscripted Monologue 💫
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
A video shot 2 years ago in a very weak moment. A moment where I channeled my emotions to creativity so it distracts me. I had just come back from a shoot & something major happened & I couldn’t stop crying. I just switched on the camera, & started speaking, hoping it would drift my mind away from what had happened. This is how it turned out. One shot, unscripted, RAW NIDHI KUMAR. Found this in my gallery last week. I’m super nervous as I even write this, but sometimes the best comes out of the worst. Thankyou @bhavika_motwani for pushing me to post this! ❤️
PS- THIS ISN’T RELATED AT ALL TO WHAT ACTUALLY HAPPENED!  Like AT ALL before y’all start thinking, lol.
PPS- My mascara, eyeliner was all over my eyes after all the crying so forgive me 😂
Hope you guys like it.
*
#monologue #unscripted #raw #unfiltered #breakup #lethergo #actor

latestPosts.caption:
#NKDCinematicUniverse >> Bollywood! -5 DEGREES on @titlis_thepeaktobe got nothing when you have the passion to create something BEAUTIFUL! Went to SWITZERLAND, the most dreamiest location in the world with @myswitzerlandar & there was NO CHANCE I WASNT GOING TO DO THIS! My dream is to take my magic to EVERY COUNTRY POSSIBLE & excuse you, after this! Where are the other countries at? 😂👀 I am just recovering from food poisoning & I promised myself, if it’s too difficult, I won’t do it, we packed my saree & GOD WAS WITH US! The sun shining straight at me & #KuttoKiTarahMehnat made this happen! @adityabhansali_ MY GENIUS FRIEND! His ideas & vision, who wants to see us work together more? @yrf @shreyaghoshal @salimsulaimanmusic 

Mom started crying so much after watching the final edit! we both asked her why! She said I look like a Bollywood heroine (her dream) , saw how hard we were working, you were freezing but you didn’t stop! & I could see you both work in Switzerland while I was siting inside in between the mountains 🥹🥹🥹✨💪🙏🧿 @visitlucerne @travelswitzerland_official @altayerholidays #mylucerne 

PS - all angrez peeps kept shooting me & kept asking “aren’t you freezing lol” 😂 ALSO, MET A #NIDHISFAM HERE, what are the odds? 

Shot & edited by @adityabhansali_ ❤️✨

#NKDinSwitzerland #travel #travelinfluencer
